summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Uruguay shipping form application. All backend APIs and frontend functionality working perfectly. Tested form submission, validation, Excel exports, CRUD operations, and UI integration.
passed_tests: All 11 backend API endpoints working correctly
Form loads with all required fields (ticket, calle, numero, telefono, contacto, departamento, motivo)
Departamento dropdown shows all 19 Uruguay departments
Motivo dropdown shows 3 options (Entrega, Retiro y Entrega, Retiro)
Form validation working for all required fields
Table displays records with real-time updates
Export buttons functional for individual and bulk downloads
Success notifications and error handling working
